## 11. QUALITY CONTROL CHECK (MANDATORY)

Before closing Gate 6, verify:
- All prior Gates are executed
- No new evidence or analysis is introduced
- Risks are clearly categorized and justified
- Decision logic is explicit
- Excel is complete and consistent
- Word reflects Excel outcomes accurately

